data.description: 350&348 Ashley ST. Welcome to this beautiful home located in the Four Lakes Community! This spacious 4bed/2bath home has an open floor plan with cathedral ceilings. There are hardwood floors throughout the living,dining,and kitchen areas and plush carpets in the bedrooms. This home includes the lot next door, 348 Ashley St, both parcels together total 1.73-acres and is zoned agricultural. The property includes a chicken shed with fenced in pen, raised garden beds, and lots of room for your family to enjoy! If you like to fish this home is located less than a mile from Holden Park boat ramp. This home will be perfect for your family,come see it today! Call listing agents for any questions.
